Detailed Description

This async event is in response to the command (RL_DEV_CONFIG_SET_MSG: RL_DEV_RX_DATA_PATH_CONF_SET_SB) which indicates ADC data needs to be transferred over SPI. This async event contains the ADC data followed by more such async events for additional data. SB-ID : RL_DEV_AE_MSS_ADC_DATA_SB.
